  26:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dcmipp.c ****                         ##### How to use this driver #####
  27:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dcmipp.c ****   ==============================================================================
  28:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dcmipp.c ****   [..]
  29:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dcmipp.c ****      The sequence below describes how to use this driver to capture image
  30:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dcmipp.c ****      from a camera module connected to the DCMIPP Interface.
  31:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dcmipp.c ****      This sequence does not take into account the configuration of the
  32:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dcmipp.c ****      camera module, which should be made before to configure and enable
  33:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dcmipp.c ****      the DCMIPP to capture images.
  34:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dcmipp.c **** 
  35:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dcmipp.c **** 
  36:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dcmipp.c **** 
  37:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dcmipp.c **** Initialize the DCMIPP and the CSI through HAL_DCMIPP_Init() function.
  38:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dcmipp.c **** 
  39:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dcmipp.c ****   *** Mandatory Configuration ***
  40:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dcmipp.c ****   ===================================
  41:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dcmipp.c **** The configuration of the camera sensor interface, in Parallel or CSI (Camera Serial Interface) mode
  42:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dcmipp.c **** involves programming specific parameters to ensure proper functionality.
  43:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dcmipp.c **** Below is the structured process for configuring each interface type:
  44:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dcmipp.c **** 
  45:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dcmipp.c ****      (#)Parallel Mode configuration
  46:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dcmipp.c ****         To configure the camera sensor in Parallel mode, program the following parameters:
  47:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dcmipp.c ****         the Format, the VSPolarity,the HSPolarity, the PCKPolarity, the ExtendedDataMode the Synchr
  48:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dcmipp.c ****         the SynchroCodes of the frame delimiter, the SwapBits and the SwapCycles
  49:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dcmipp.c ****         using HAL_DCMIPP_PARALLEL_SetConfig() function.
  50:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dcmipp.c **** 
  51:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dcmipp.c ****      (#)Serial Mode configuration (CSI)
  52:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dcmipp.c ****         To configure the camera in Serial mode, use the following functions to set the correspondin
  53:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dcmipp.c ****          + The NumberOfLanes, the DataLaneMapping and the PHYBitrate using HAL_DCMIPP_CSI_SetConfig
  54:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dcmipp.c ****          + The DataTypeFormat for the selected Virtual Channel HAL_DCMIPP_CSI_SetVCConfig() functio
  55:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dcmipp.c ****            the DataTypeNB, the DataTypeClass and the DataTypeFormat for the selected Virtual Channe
  56:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dcmipp.c ****            using HAL_DCMIPP_CSI_SetVCFilteringConfig() function.
  57:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dcmipp.c ****          + The DataTypeMode, the DataTypeIDA, the DataTypeIDB using HAL_DCMIPP_CSI_PIPE_SetConfig()
  58:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dcmipp.c **** 
  59:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dcmipp.c ****      (#)Pipe configuration
  60:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dcmipp.c **** Regardless of the interface type, the pipe configuration is necessary:
  61:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dcmipp.c ****          + To configure the Pipe , program the following parameters:
  62:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dcmipp.c ****            the FrameRate, the PixelPipePitch and PixelPackerFormat for pixel Pipes using
  63:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dcmipp.c ****            HAL_DCMIPP_PIPE_SetConfig() function.
  64:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dcmipp.c **** 
  65:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dcmipp.c ****      (#)Default Shared Data Flow
  66:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dcmipp.c ****         By default, or by invoking HAL_DCMIPP_PIPE_CSI_EnableShare() ,the dataflow of PIPE1 is shar
  67:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dcmipp.c ****         In this case the VC and DataType are the same as those configured for PIPE1 thus
  68:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dcmipp.c ****         data acquistion can be started for PIPE2 without any additional configuration.
  69:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dcmipp.c ****      (#)Disabling Shared Data Flow
  70:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dcmipp.c ****         The shared dataflow between Pixel Pipes can be disabled by calling HAL_DCMIPP_PIPE_CSI_Disa
  71:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dcmipp.c ****         This action must be performed before starting data acquisition on either pipe
  72:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dcmipp.c ****         In this case the VC and DataType must be configured for Pipe2 separately.
  73:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dcmipp.c **** 
  74:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dcmipp.c ****   *** Interrupt mode IO operation ***
  75:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dcmipp.c ****   ===================================
  76:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dcmipp.c **** 
  77:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dcmipp.c ****     (##) Parallel Mode
  78:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dcmipp.c ****      (#) Configure Pipe parameters, destination (one or two) and Capture Mode (Snapshot or Continuo
  79:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dcmipp.c ****          the capture request using one from the following functions:
  80:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dcmipp.c ****          HAL_DCMIPP_PIPE_Start() or HAL_DCMIPP_PIPE_DoubleBufferStart().
  81:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dcmipp.c **** 
