  99:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dcmipp.c **** 
 100:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dcmipp.c ****          Configure DCMIPP_PIPE1, Virtual Channel, destination addresses (Y, U and V addresses) and 
 101:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dcmipp.c ****         (Snapshot or Continuous) and enable the capture request for Semi-planar buffer
 102:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dcmipp.c ****          using the following functions:
 103:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dcmipp.c ****          HAL_DCMIPP_CSI_PIPE_FullPlanarStart() or HAL_DCMIPP_CSI_PIPE_FullPlanarDoubleBufferStart()
 104:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dcmipp.c **** 
 105:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dcmipp.c ****      (#) Use HAL_DCMIPP_IRQHandler() called under DCMIPP_IRQHandler() interrupt subroutine.
 106:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dcmipp.c ****      (#) At the end of frame capture request HAL_DCMIPP_IRQHandler() function is executed and user 
 107:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dcmipp.c ****          add his own function by customization of function pointer PipeFrameEventCallback (member
 108:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dcmipp.c ****          of DCMIPP handle structure).
 109:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dcmipp.c **** 
 110:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dcmipp.c ****    (#) Use HAL_DCMIPP_CSI_IRQHandler() called under CSI_IRQHandler() interrupt subroutine.
 111:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dcmipp.c ****    (#) At the start or the end of frame capture HAL_DCMIPP_CSI_IRQHandler() function is executed an
 112:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dcmipp.c ****        add his own function by customization of function pointer StartOfFrameEventCallback or EndOf
 113:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dcmipp.c **** 
 114:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dcmipp.c ****     (#) In case of common error, the HAL_DCMIPP_IRQHandler() function calls the callback
 115:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dcmipp.c ****          ErrorCallback, in case of Pipe error the HAL_DCMIPP_IRQHandler() function calls the callba
 116:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dcmipp.c ****      and in case of CSI Line error the HAL_DCMIPP_CSI_IRQHandler() function calls the callback
 117:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dcmipp.c ****          LineErrorCallback.
 118:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dcmipp.c **** 
 119:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dcmipp.c ****     (#) The Pipe capture can be suspended and resumed using the following functions
 120:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dcmipp.c ****         HAL_DCMIPP_PIPE_Suspend() and HAL_DCMIPP_PIPE_Resume().
 121:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dcmipp.c **** 
 122:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dcmipp.c ****     (#) For Snapshot Mode the capture can be re-enabled using the HAL_DCMIPP_PIPE_EnableCapture();
 123:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dcmipp.c **** 
 124:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dcmipp.c ****     (#) Optionally, Program the required configuration through the following parameters:
 125:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dcmipp.c ****         Client, MemoryPageSize, Traffic, MaxOutstandingTransactions, DPREGStart, DPREGEnd
 126:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dcmipp.c ****         and WLRURatio using HAL_DCMIPP_SetIPPlugConfig().
 127:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dcmipp.c **** 
